					 National 12.</p>
					 
					<p>See <a href="./calendar.html">Calendar</a> for a full list of events.</p>

					<p>Races are sailed under the current 
					<a href="http://www.sailing.org/racingrules.php" target="_blank">Racing Rules of Sailing (RRS)</a> 
					laid down by International Sailing Federation (ISAF) and the 
					requirements of the Club's Sailing Instructions.
					</p>
					 
